@startuml
title Registrierung

' --- Mermaid-ähnlicher Style ---
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI, Trebuchet MS, sans-serif"
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #333333
  ArrowThickness 1.5
  LifeLineBorderColor #AAAAAA
  LifeLineBorderThickness 1.5
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

  ParticipantBorderColor #AAAAAA
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #ECECFF
  ParticipantFontColor #333333
  ParticipantBorderThickness 1.5
  ParticipantPadding 12

  ActorBorderColor #AAAAAA
  ActorBackgroundColor #ECECFF
  ActorFontColor #333333

  BoxBorderColor #BBBBBB
  BoxBackgroundColor #F9F9FF
  BoxFontColor #666666
  BoxFontSize 12

  DividerBorderColor #CCCCCC
  DividerBackgroundColor #F0F0F0

  MessageAlign center
}

skinparam title {
  FontSize 16
  FontColor #333333
  BorderRoundCorner 10
  BorderColor #CCCCCC
  BackgroundColor #ECECFF
}
' --- Ende Style ---

actor "Versicherte Person" as Person
box "Smartphone App"
participant "Smartphone App" as App
participant "ZETA Client" as ZETA
participant "Gesundheits-ID Authenticator" as Authenticator
end box
participant "Email-Account" as Email

box "Telematik-Infrastruktur"
participant "Sektoraler IDP" as IDP
participant "ZETA Guard" as Guard
end box

Person -> App: start app
App -> ZETA: authenticate
ZETA -> Authenticator: authenticate
Authenticator -> IDP: authorize call am Sek-IDP
IDP --> Authenticator: credentials abfragen
Authenticator --> Person: credentials abfragen
Person -> Authenticator: credentials eingeben 
Authenticator -> IDP: credentials
IDP --> Authenticator: id_token ausstellen
Authenticator --> ZETA: id_token ausstellen

App -> Person: E-Mail abfragen
Person -> App: E-Mail eingaben
App -> ZETA: register
ZETA -> Guard: register
Guard -> Email: One Time Passwort versenden
Person -> Email: E-Mail mit One Time Passwort abrufen
Email --> Person: Email mit One Time Passwort
Person -> App: One Time Passwort eingeben
App -> ZETA: One Time Passwort
ZETA -> Guard:  One Time Passwort

@enduml
